ntainer\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ad3e20d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ad3e20d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Work With a Professional Team<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-949782b elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"949782b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-91dea95 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"91dea95\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>We are proud to introduce our talented and experienced team.With over 15 years of development, our company has grown into a highly professional and dedicated group. Our packaging specialists bring more than 15 years of industry expertise to every project.The team includes:5 Mechanical Engineers with over 15 years of experience in designing and developing liquid bottling equipment\uff1b3 Electrical Engineers skilled in PLC and motion controllers, responsible for programming and integrating full bottling line systems\uff1b3 After-sales Service Engineers, each with more than 5 years of experience in training, installation, and commissioning\u2014all proficient in English to ensure smooth communication with global clients.Together, we deliver innovative and reliable packaging solutions tailored to your needs.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e8e50bd e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\"